{"title":"Mondraker Summum DH bike goes carbon, MINDs its suspension with digital tracking","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/08/mondraker-summum-dh-bike-goes-carbon-minds-its-suspension-with-digital-tracking/","date":1623160841000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Introduced <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/09/01/2021-mondraker-summum-races-dh-w-stealth-alloy-frame-27-5-29-wheels-or-both/\">in alloy form last fall</a> after taking a number of top spots on the downhill world stage (it swept the podium at the Val di Sol World Championships), the new Mondraker Summum Carbon DH bike brings all of the brand’s top level tech to the gravity game.</p><p>It keeps their Forward Geometry, which puts the shortest possible stem on the bike, and uses their lightweight Stealth Air Carbon frame construction. It even gets their Zero suspension, but with a new design based around a Trunnion shock.</p><p>But the most important update is the addition of their MIND suspension telemetry kit, letting you track your suspension’s activity over a GPS map to see where, when, and how it’s working so you can tune it better than ever.</p><h2>2022 Mondraker Summum Carbon tech details</h2><figure id=\"attachment_261331\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261331\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2.jpg\" alt=\"2022 mondraker summum carbon rr downhil bike frame details\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amaz