www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085853/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-2-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261331\">Even the fork bumpers are streamlined into the top tube.</figcaption></figure><p>The new Summum Carbon bike comes in two variants, R and RR, but the difference is spec. They share the same Stealth Air Carbon frame with a streamlined look. Mondraker says they wanted to give it a lean, lightweight look and feel compared to the sometimes bulky-looking bikes found on the mountain.</p><p>So, they followed the lines of their trail and enduro mountain bikes to give the Summum a slimmer look. But with the addition of a Trunnion shock mount and good engineering, they maintained the stiffness and strength needed to handle World Cup downhill courses.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1.jpg\" alt=\"2022 mondraker summum carbon rr downhil bike suspension shown from top\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-629x420.jpg 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085847/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-1-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><p>They also added a new one-piece, full-carbon monoblock upper linkage, and surrounded the rear shock in a cage to maximize lateral rigidity.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7.jpg\" alt=\"2022 mondraker summum carbon rr downhil bike suspension shown from left side\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-629x420.jpg 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085931/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-7-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><p>The Zero suspension platform uses a closed rear triangle with upper and lower linkages. What makes it unique is that the shock passes through the seat tube and connects with the lower linkage just behind the tube, giving it fully floating design where the shock isn’t directly mounted to the frame at all.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><h3>It has a MIND of its own</h3><p><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis\" width=\"1500\" height=\"975\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-297x193.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-800x520.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-120x78.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-768x499.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-696x452.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-1068x694.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-646x420.jpg 646w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-297x193.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-800x520.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-120x78.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-768x499.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-696x452.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-1068x694.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_detail-646x420.jpg 646w\"></a></p><p>Notice those two little holes above the main upper pivot on the photo before this one? Those are the mounting spots for the Mondraker MIND diagnostics tool. Attach it, and it’ll track your suspension’s movement and air time, synced with your position on a track thanks to GPS. You can then analyze the data in their smartphone app to compare changes in tune and setup to get the fastest time. Check <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/09/mondraker-mind-integrated-telemetry-tool-perfects-easy-intuitive-suspension-setup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our full tech coverage of MIND</a> for more details.</p><h2><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span>Summum Carbon Build Specs &amp; Geometry</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6.jpg\" alt=\"2022 mondraker summum carbon rr downhil bike going off a jump\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/08085923/2022-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-tech-details-6-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2